{"tid":1425583,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急!!!Facebook依家要自影大頭去認證自己既咩？？？","createTime":"2019-08-06T18:50:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T00:13:05.000Z","uid":28921,"like":105,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"38dd23895e876369ce2d70d6c185958940c42851","tid":1425583,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:50:58.000Z","msg":"話說，我呢個Facebook ac用左好多年，不嬲淨係link落我舊email到<br />\n<br />\n突然間睇睇下立場直播就彈左呢個出黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4niBrHb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4niBrHb.png&h=50ab044c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後就叫你入電話號碼，再收個認證碼<br />\n咁真係太心急想睇立場直播，就快手入左自己電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後，叫我upload自己幅相去證明係本人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Po9H6HX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPo9H6HX.png&h=45c4371c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嚇撚到我，屌佢老母，依家乜撚野事，要自影大頭咁撚on9。<br />\n不過，當然無upload啦，點撚知會唔會俾人賣俾狗共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢d私隱，就算銀行apps都唔會要你個大頭upload上去個apps啦dllm<br />\n<br />\n但近排可能Facebook 屌人屌得太多，由其今日屌個大左膠何式凝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，俾人report 左？<br />\n<br />\n我早幾日仲收到個無來電顯示既錄音，聲稱係中國移動打嚟，話我電話使用有問題，兩個鐘之後就暫停電話服務，但重點係，我唔係用中國移動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲可以解答，定係我要下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a588a8ca01e99475f1968c4a11673c9f28ae8e5","tid":1425583,"uid":28921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"57aa400feed7e57b40ff915393c5b8f1ff87cfbd","tid":1425583,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6473b2102943b228d4291382a90d0cc25ee8a02","tid":1425583,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957ca17236dc7aa44f5d1369c2604ae46f71deb0","tid":1425583,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6eef4cac5400fdaf0f66366311b4b8561fae7bb","tid":1425583,"uid":157152,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"一樣比人封左，Facebook宜家係味宣布奶共？"},{"pid":"5a4cf30f83b31e20625be8238ebd54b55191e3bc","tid":1425583,"uid":157994,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"fb總部親中，fb亞洲部會ban反中言論as racist, 完。"},{"pid":"8cc381a34680cc4762d63784b928cc882ddc112d","tid":1425583,"uid":148181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:52:57.000Z","msg":"遇到同樣問題 唔敢做任何野住 睇睇下fb live就咁樣"},{"pid":"99daa1295cf61bc3ef2e5ea8b1aa998505e749a7","tid":1425583,"uid":28921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/danc