<br />\n<br />\n我早幾日仲收到個無來電顯示既錄音，聲稱係中國移動打嚟，話我電話使用有問題，兩個鐘之後就暫停電話服務，但重點係，我唔係用中國移動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲可以解答，定係我要下世小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T04:27:51.000Z","msg":"你講個個中移動我早幾日都收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係有關??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nps 面書已被封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e4d0e39aef1dff17ee35b237f3336da7a80ab9","tid":1425583,"uid":219984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"dacd9d58856771e0ec3c885dc00507bc4e40c1ab","tid":1425583,"uid":275366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"dllm facebook"},{"pid":"5fd978498fa37ffe91276259f53e74fd9985d913","tid":1425583,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"全港一齊轉用Twitter 啦<br />\nTwitter 一樣可以做直播<br />\n仲可以同美國日本用戶接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f2cd93adc6f59c667d2821b25cdcf733a43e74e","tid":1425583,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"中國移動嗰個我都收過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得似係騙案，因為我都唔係用中國移動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cef600ac017699e0ff2f873b2a826243bce2014","tid":1425583,"uid":265734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:17:22.000Z","msg":"淨係知ig係會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63de0f0cbfaad06959047df9da0f64d31507d6c3","tid":1425583,"uid":12512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:19:53.000Z","msg":"fb依家唯一用處